            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Understanding MCP explains why AI tools are rapidly gaining real-time data capabilities. For marketing teams building AI workflows, MCP is the underlying standard that determines which tools your AI assistant can connect to and what actions it can take.</p></div></div>
          </div>
